Gregory Darnell CURTIS, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Katrice LEE, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2102 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. OCTOBER 12, 2017

ORDERED that appellant's motion to withdraw appeal is granted, and this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is hereby dismissed.
